OL,6,                        S     p~t0     
OL,7,BTV presenterEJosie D'Arby,Bwho stars in
OL,8,BAladdin at the Hackney Empire says:    
OL,10,B"People slag off panto and I had my    
OL,11,Bdoubts about Aladdin as it's my first  
OL,12,Bone. But your whole attitude changes   
OL,13,Bwhen you see the kids' smiling faces." 
OL,15,BDancerELionel BlairBsays: "I get really
OL,16,Bannoyed whenBpeople knock panto. It's  
OL,17,Bnot justBactors mucking about. It's a  
OL,18,Bprecise artBform, closer to restoration
OL,19,Bcomedy thanBjust a throwaway farce."   
